  ('cpa-moex-01231', 'cpa', 'cpa-moex-104-17b9ba7b', 'sub-cpa-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '在分步成本制度下，計算約當單位成本時可採用加權平均法或先進先出法。試問在何種情況下，兩 法所計得的約當單位成本會相同？', '["無期初在製品，有期末在製品", "有期初在製品，無期末在製品", "有期初在製品，有期末在製品", "兩法下的約當單位成本不可能會相同"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:29:13+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "3bf055ad8f6f", "answer_pdf_sha1": "e8f11787a170", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "104130", "c": "803", "s": "0205", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "成本會計與管理會計", "year": "104", "exam_name": "104年專門職業及技術人員高等考試會計師、不動產估價師、專利師考試", "original_question_number": 13, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "accountant", "db_exam_id": "cpa"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('cpa-moex-01232', 'cpa', 'cpa-moex-104-17b9ba7b', 'sub-cpa-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '大方公司之總資產為$600,000，剩餘利潤為$375,000，必要報酬率為12%，營業淨利率為15%，則該 公司之銷貨收入為：', '["$2,500,000", "$2,980,000", "$3,875,000", "$5,000,000"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:29:13+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "3bf055ad8f6f", "answer_pdf_sha1": "e8f11787a170", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "104130", "c": "803", "s": "0205", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "成本會計與管理會計", "year": "104", "exam_name": "104年專門職業及技術人員高等考試會計師、不動產估價師、專利師考試", "original_question_number": 14, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "accountant", "db_exam_id": "cpa"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('cpa-moex-01233', 'cpa', 'cpa-moex-104-17b9ba7b', 'sub-cpa-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '建立平衡計分卡制度的第一個步驟是：', '["研究顧客的需求", "選擇組織所欲達成的獲利水準", "釐清組織的任務與願景", "瞭解市場的趨勢與變化"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:29:13+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "3bf055ad8f6f", "answer_pdf_sha1": "e8f11787a170", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "104130", "c": "803", "s": "0205", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "成本會計與管理會計", "year": "104", "exam_name": "104年專門職業及技術人員高等考試會計師、不動產估價師、專利師考試", "original_question_number": 15, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "accountant", "db_exam_id": "cpa"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('cpa-moex-01234', 'cpa', 'cpa-moex-104-17b9ba7b', 'sub-cpa-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '東原事業單位正在規劃下一年度的營業預算，目標投資報酬率為20%，預計銷售量為5,000單位，變 動成本率為 60%，固定成本為$70,000，公司要求的最低報酬率為 15%，若欲達成$20,000 的剩餘利 潤，則每單位產品的售價應為：', '["$55", "$75", "$80", "$90"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:29:13+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "3bf055ad8f6f", "answer_pdf_sha1": "e8f11787a170", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "104130", "c": "803", "s": "0205", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "成本會計與管理會計", "year": "104", "exam_name": "104年專門職業及技術人員高等考試會計師、不動產估價師、專利師考試", "original_question_number": 16, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "accountant", "db_exam_id": "cpa"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('cpa-moex-01235', 'cpa', 'cpa-moex-104-17b9ba7b', 'sub-cpa-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '在平衡計分卡中，下列何者是學習與成長構面指標所欲衡量的內容：①組織是否鼓勵員工提供改善', '["組織是否給員工適當的授權", "組織是否能提供顧客良好的售後服務", "僅", "正確"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:29:13+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "3bf055ad8f6f", "answer_pdf_sha1": "e8f11787a170", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "104130", "c": "803", "s": "0205", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "成本會計與管理會計", "year": "104", "exam_name": "104年專門職業及技術人員高等考試會計師、不動產估價師、專利師考試", "original_question_number": 17, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "accountant", "db_exam_id": "cpa"}'::jsonb, NULL),
